soluble antioxidant. ?is study demonstrated that the chain

rameter for the use of edible oils as a nutritional supplement,
the content of each tocopherol acting as antioxidant agent,
and the phytosterol in tree-borne seed oils as cholesterol-

study will be useful parameters for the reﬁning process of tree-
